Prompting gets the AI started, but Context Engineering gets it right. 💡
​For Day 5 of my Claude AI journey, I dove into why context is the unsung hero of Generative AI. It’s the difference between a generic answer and a highly personalized, accurate business solution.
​The Golden Rule:
❌ A prompt tells the AI what to do.
✅ Context tells the AI what it needs to know before doing it.
​If you want fewer AI hallucinations and more consistent, reliable outputs, it's time to shift focus toward how you design your data environments.
